{"title":"Bolt of Draining","url":"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/Bolt_of_Draining","type":"markdown","data":"***Version [0.30](/0.30 \"0.30\")**: This article **may not be** up to date for the [latest stable release](/0.32 \"0.32\") of Crawl.*\n\n|   |                                                                                          |\n| - | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n|   | Fires a penetrating bolt of negative energy which drains any living creature it strikes. |\n\n**Bolt of Draining** is a monster-only spell which fires a bolt of [negative energy](/Negative_energy \"Negative energy\"), dealing damage and [draining](/Draining \"Draining\") any creatures in its path. For players, energy resistance reduces the damage and draining dealt by this spell by 50% (rN+), 75% (rN++), or 100% (rN+++). Draining can be quite irritating, since it lowers your max HP (until you gain sufficient XP).\n\nThe following enemies cast Bolt of Draining:\n\n- e [![Deep elf death mage.png](/images/5/5f/Deep_elf_death_mage.png)](/File:Deep_elf_death_mage.png) **[Deep elf death mage](/Deep_elf_death_mage \"Deep elf death mage\")** (3d22 damage)\n- 6 [![Demonspawn black sun.png](/images/3/39/Demonspawn_black_sun.png)](/File:Demonspawn_black_sun.png) **[Demonspawn black sun](/Demonspawn_black_sun \"Demonspawn black sun\")** (3d22 damage)\n- W [![Eidolon.png](/images/1/1d/Eidolon.png)](/File:Eidolon.png) **[Eidolon](/Eidolon \"Eidolon\")** (3d21 damage)\n- L [![Halazid warlock.png](/images/d/d2/Halazid_warlock.png)](/File:Halazid_warlock.png) **[Halazid warlock](/Halazid_warlock \"Halazid warlock\")** (3d25 damage)\n- H [![Jorogumo.png](/images/d/d1/Jorogumo.png)](/File:Jorogumo.png) **[Jorogumo](/Jorogumo \"Jorogumo\")** (3d20 damage)\n- z [![Laughing skull.png](/images/4/42/Laughing_skull.png)](/File:Laughing_skull.png) **[Laughing skull](/Laughing_skull \"Laughing skull\")** (3d(13-26) damage)\n- p [![Necromancer.png](/images/5/5d/Necromancer.png)](/File:Necromancer.png) **[Necromancer (monster)](/Necromancer_\\(monster\\) \"Necromancer (monster)\")** (3d18 damage)\n- o [![Nergalle.png](/images/9/9b/Nergalle.png)](/File:Nergalle.png) **[Nergalle](/Nergalle \"Nergalle\")** (3d18 damage)\n- o [![Orc sorcerer.png](/images/c/c6/Orc_sorcerer.png)](/File:Orc_sorcerer.png) **[Orc sorcerer](/Orc_sorcerer \"Orc sorcerer\")** (3d17 damage)\n- D [![Serpent of Hell (Tartarus).png](/images/e/e7/Serpent_of_Hell_%28Tartarus%29.png)](/File:Serpent_of_Hell_\\(Tartarus\\).png) **[Serpent of Hell (Tartarus)](/Serpent_of_Hell_\\(Tartarus\\) \"Serpent of Hell (Tartarus)\")** (3d24 damage)\n- D [![Shadow dragon.png](/images/3/3a/Shadow_dragon.png)](/File:Shadow_dragon.png) **[Shadow dragon](/Shadow_dragon \"Shadow dragon\")** (3d24 damage)\n- 1 [![Tzitzimitl.png](/images/0/02/Tzitzimitl.png)](/File:Tzitzimitl.png) **[Tzitzimitl](/Tzitzimitl \"Tzitzimitl\")** (3d29 damage)\n- V [![Vampire mage.png](/images/9/94/Vampire_mage.png)](/File:Vampire_mage.png) **[Vampire mage](/Vampire_mage \"Vampire mage\")** (3d18 damage)\n\nThe following enemies may be able to cast Bolt of Draining, depending on their spell set:\n\n- & [![Pandemonium lord.png](/images/c/c6/Pandemonium_lord.png)](/File:Pandemonium_lord.png) **[Pandemonium lord](/Pandemonium_lord \"Pandemonium lord\")** (5.2% chance)\n\n## History\n\n| [![Bolt of draining.png](/images/6/6b/Bolt_of_draining.png)](/File:Bolt_of_draining.png) Bolt of Draining |                                                   |\n| :-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------- |\n| Level                                                                                                     | 5                                                 |\n| School1                                                                                                   | [Conjuration](/Conjurations \"Conjurations\")       |\n| School2                                                                                                   | [Necromancy](/Necromancy \"Necromancy\")            |\n| Source(s)                                                                                                 | - [Book of Death](/Book_of_Death \"Book of Death\") |\n| [Casting noise](/Spell_noise \"Spell noise\")                                                               | 2                                                 |\n| [Spell noise](/Spell_noise \"Spell noise\")                                                                 | 0                                                 |\n\n| Spell Details                           |                                                            |\n| :-------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------- |\n| Damage Formula                          | 4d(3.75+Power\\*3/20)                                       |\n| Max Damage                              | 4d33 [negative energy](/Negative_energy \"Negative energy\") |\n| [Max Power](/Spell_power \"Spell power\") | 200                                                        |\n| Range                                   | 6                                                          |\n| Targeting                               | Bolt                                                       |\n| To-hit                                  | 8+Power/20                                                 |\n| Special                                 | [Draining](/Draining \"Draining\")                           |\n\n- Prior to [0.26](/0.26 \"0.26\"), [draining](/Drain \"Drain\") reduced skill XP instead of max HP. Also, [bolt spells](/Bolt_spell \"Bolt spell\") had their range reduced by 1 for each target they hit.\n- Prior to [0.25](/0.25 \"0.25\"), Bolt of Draining was a level 5 [Conjurations](/Conjurations \"Conjurations\")/[Necromancy](/Necromancy \"Necromancy\") spell available to players.\n- Prior to [0.14](/0.14 \"0.14\"), Bolt of Draining was a level 6 spell.\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Bolt of Draining - CrawlWiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Bolt_of_Draining\",\"wgTitle\":\"Bolt of Draining\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":70742,\"wgRevisionId\":70742,\"wgArticleId\":334,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"0.30 articles\",\"Conjuration Spells\",\"Necromancy Spells\",\"Level 5 Spells\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort\":[\"\",\"Jan\",\"Feb\",\"Mar\",\"Apr\",\"May\",\"Jun\",\"Jul\",\"Aug\",\"Sep\",\"Oct\",\"Nov\",\"Dec\"],\"wgRelevantPageName\":\"Bolt_of_Draining\",\"wgRelevantArticleId\":334,\"wgRequestId\":\"fbaf382c69ee57a262739640\",\"wgIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRelevantPageIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRestrictionEdit\":[],\"wgRestrictionMove\":[]});mw.loader.state({\"site.styles\":\"ready\",\"noscript\":\"ready\",\"user.styles\":\"ready\",\"user\":\"ready\",\"user.options\":\"loading\",\"user.tokens\":\"loading\",\"ext.smw.style\":\"ready\",\"ext.smw.tooltip.styles\":\"ready\",\"mediawiki.legacy.shared\":\"ready\",\"mediawiki.legacy.commonPrint\":\"ready\",\"mediawiki.sectionAnc