 mw-hide-empty-elt ns-0 ns-subject page-Bolt_of_Draining rootpage-Bolt_of_Draining skin-vector action-view\">\t\t<div id=\"mw-page-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"mw-head-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"mw-body\" role=\"main\">\n\t\t<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n\t\twindow.google_analytics_uacct = \"UA-3380984-8\";\n</script>\n<div class=\"adsense\">\n\t\t<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\n\t\tgoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-7088061744296615\";\n\t\t/* CrawlWiki skyscraper */\n\t\tgoogle_ad_slot = \"8196155564\";\n\t\tgoogle_ad_width = 160;\n\t\tgoogle_ad_height = 600;\n-->\n</script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n\t\t\t<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Bolt of Draining</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From CrawlWiki</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\" class=\"mw-jump\">\n\t\t\t\t\tJump to:\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#mw-head\">navigation</a>, \t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#p-search\">search</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"border: 1px solid #f90; background-color: #fc6; border-left: 15px solid #f90; margin-bottom: 20px; width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; line-height: 1.1em; width: auto;\"><i><b>Version <a href=\"/0.30\" title=\"0.30\">0.30</a></b>: This article <b>may not be</b> up to date for the <a href=\"/0.32\" title=\"0.32\">latest stable release</a> of Crawl.</i></div>\n<table style=\"background:#f5faff; border:1px solid #cedff2; width:auto; margin: 0px 5%; margin-bottom:1.25em; font-style:italic; text-align:left; color:#000; padding:1.5em 1em;\">\n\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"> Fires a penetrating bolt of negative energy which drains any living creature it strikes.\n</td></tr></table>\n<p><b>Bolt of Draining</b> is a monster-only spell which fires a bolt of <a href=\"/Negative_energy\" title=\"Negative energy\">negative energy</a>, dealing damage and <a href=\"/Draining\" title=\"Draining\">draining</a> any creatures in its path. For players, energy resistance reduces the damage and draining dealt by this spell by 50% (rN+), 75% (rN++), or 100% (rN+++). Draining can be quite irritating, since it lowers your max HP (until you gain sufficient XP).\n</p><p>The following enemies cast Bolt of Draining:\n</p>\n<ul><li> <span class=\"nhsym clr-white\">e</span> <a href=\"/File:Deep_elf_death_mage.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Deep elf death mage.png\" src=\"/images/5/5f/Deep_elf_death_mage.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Deep_elf_death_mage\" title=\"Deep elf death mage\">Deep elf death mage</a></b> (3d22 damage)</li>\n<li> <span class=\"nhsym clr-brightmagenta\">6</span> <a href=\"/File:Demonspawn_black_sun.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Demonspawn black sun.png\" src=\"/images/3/39/Demonspawn_black_sun.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Demonspawn_black_sun\" title=\"Demonspawn black sun\">Demonspawn black sun</a></b> (3d22 damage)</li>\n<li> <span class=\"nhsym clr-brown\">W</span> <a href=\"/File:Eidolon.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Eidolon.png\" src=\"/images/1/1d/Eidolon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Eidolon\" title=\"Eidolon\">Eidolon</a></b> (3d21 damage)</li>\n<li> <span class=\"nhsym clr-green\">L</span> <a href=\"/File:Halazid_warlock.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Halazid warlock.png\" src=\"/images/d/d2/Halazid_warlock.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Halazid_warlock\" title=\"Halazid warlock\">Halazid warlock</a></b> (3d25 damage)</li>\n<li> <span class=\"nhsym\" style=\"color: #1c1ce7\">H</span> <a href=\"/File:Jorogumo.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Jorogumo.png\" src=\"/images/d/d1/Jorogumo.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Jorogumo\" title=\"Jorogumo\">Jorogumo</a></b> (3d20 damage)</li>\n<li> <span class=\"nhsym\" style=\"color: #ff5555\">z</span> <a href=\"/File:Laughing_skull.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Laughing skull.png\" src=\"/images/4/42/Laughing_skull.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Laughing_skull\" title=\"Laughing skull\">Laughing skull</a></b> (3d(13-26) damage)</li>\n<li> <span class=\"nhsym clr-white\">p</span> <a href=\"/File:Necromancer.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Necromancer.png\" src=\"/images/5/5d/Necromancer.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Necromancer_(monster)\" title=\"Necromancer (monster)\">Necromancer (monster)</a></b> (3d18 damage)</li>\n<li> <span class=\"nhsym clr-white\">o</span> <a href=\"/File:Nergalle.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Nergalle.png\" src=\"/images/9/9b/Nergalle.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Nergalle\" title=\"Nergalle\">Nergalle</a></b> (3d18 damage)</li>\n<li> <span class=\"nhsym clr-brightmagenta\">o</span> <a href=\"/File:Orc_sorcerer.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Orc sorcerer.png\" src=\"/images/c/c6/Orc_sorcerer.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Orc_sorcerer\" title=\"Orc sorcerer\">Orc sorcerer</a></b> (3d17 damage)</li>\n<li> <span class=\"nhsym clr-darkgray\">D</span> <a href=\"/File:Serpent_of_Hell_(Tartarus).png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Serpent of Hell (Tartarus).png\" src=\"/images/e/e7/Serpent_of_Hell_%28Tartarus%29.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"48\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Serpent_of_Hell_(Tartarus)\" title=\"Serpent of Hell (Tartarus)\">Serpent of Hell (Tartarus)</a></b> (3d24 damage)</li>\n<li> <span class=\"nhsym clr-magenta\">D</span> <a href=\"/File:Shadow_dragon.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Shadow dragon.png\" src=\"/images/3/3a/Shadow_dragon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Shadow_dragon\" title=\"Shadow dragon\">Shadow dragon</a></b> (3d24 damage)</li>\n<li> <span class=\"nhsym clr-magenta\">1</span> <a href=\"/File:Tzitzimitl.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Tzitzimitl.png\" src=\"/images/0/02/Tzitzimitl.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Tzitzimitl\" title=\"Tzitzimitl\">Tzitzimitl</a></b> (3d29 damage)</li>\n<li> <span class=\"nhsym clr-magenta\">V</span> <a href=\"/File:Vampire_mage.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Vampire mage.png\" src=\"/images/9/94/Vampire_mage.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Vampire_mage\" title=\"Vampire mage\">Vampire mage</a></b> (3d18 damage)</li></ul>\n<p>The following enemies may be able to cast Bolt of Draining, depending on their spell set:\n</p>\n<ul><li> <span class=\"nhsym\" style=\"color: #A4C592; border: 1px solid #A4C592;\">&amp;</span> <a href=\"/File:Pandemonium_lord.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Pandemonium lord.png\" src=\"/images/c/c6/Pandemonium_lord.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"48\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Pandemonium_lord\" title=\"Pandemonium lord\">Pandemonium lord</a></b> (5.2% chance)</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<div style=\"margin: 1.4em; margin-top:0; margin-right:0; padding: 0px; float: right; border:none;\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"border:none; margin:0; padding:0; width:18em;\">\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" style=\"font-size:larger;\"> <a href=\"/File:Bolt_of_draining.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Bolt of draining.png\" src=\"/images/6/6b/Bolt_of_draining.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#8195;Bolt of Draining\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Level\n</th>\n<td> 5\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> School<sup>1</sup>\n</th>\n<td> <a href=\"/Conjurations\" title=\"Conjurations\">Conjuration</a>\n</td></tr>\n\n\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> School<sup>2</sup>\n</th>\n<td> <a href=\"/Necromancy\" title=\"Necromancy\">Necromancy</a>\n</td></tr>\n\n\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Source(s)\n</th>\n<td><div>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Book_of_Death\" title=\"Book of Death\">Book of Death</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> <a href=\"/Spell_noise\" title=\"Spell noise\">Casting noise</a>\n</th>\n<td> 2\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> <a href=\"/Spell_noise\" title=\"Spell noise\">Spell noise</a>\n</th>\n<td> 0\n</td></tr>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</table></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 1.4em; margin-top:0; margin-right:0; padding: 0px; float: right; clear: right; border:none;\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"border:none; margin:0; padding:0; width:20em;\">\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" style=\"font-size:larger;\"> Spell Details\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Damage Formula\n</th>\n<td> 4d(3.75+Power*3/20)\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Max Damage\n</th>\n<td> 4d33 <a href=\"/Negative_energy\" title=\"Negative energy\">negative energy</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> <a href=\"/Spell_power\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Spell power\"> Max Power</a>\n</th>\n<td> 200\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Range\n</th>\n<td> 6\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Targeting\n</th>\n<td>Bolt\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> To-hit\n</th>\n<td>8+Power/20\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Special\n</th>\n<td> <a href=\"/Draining\" title=\"Draining\">Draining</a>\n</td></tr></table></div>\n<ul><li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.26\" title=\"0.26\">0.26</a>, <a href=\"/Drain\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Drain\">draining</a> reduced skill XP instead of max HP. Also, <a href=\"/Bolt_spell\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bolt spell\">bolt spells</a> had their range reduced by 1 for each target they hit.</li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.25\" title=\"0.25\">0.25</a>, Bolt of Draining was a level 5 <a href=\"/Conjurations\" title=\"Conjurations\">Conjurations</a>/<a href=\"/Necromancy\" title=\"Necromancy\">Necromancy</a> spell available to players.<