get = Bolt\n|tohit = 8+Power/20\n|special = [[Draining]]\n|hit_type = normal\n|hit_adder = 8\n|hit_num = 1\n|hit_denom = 20\n|dam_calculator = calcdice\n|dam_numdice = 4\n|dam_adder = 15\n|dam_num = 3\n|dam_denom = 5}}\n*Prior to [[0.26]], [[drain]]ing reduced skill XP instead of max HP. Also, [[bolt spell]]s had their range reduced by 1 for each target they hit.\n*Prior to [[0.25]], Bolt of Draining was a level 5 [[Conjurations]]/[[Necromancy]] spell available to players.\n*Prior to [[0.14]], Bolt of Draining was a level 6 spell."}